dc_title_s: Carte de France et des frontiéres ä 1/200.000 (Type 1912)
dc_description_s: Shows Longwy and surrounding region.; Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights.; Shows railroads, tramways, rivers, canals, bridges, towers, ruins, fortifications, and windmills.; Longitude on map assumes Paris as prime meridian.|42 x 66 centimeters, on sheet 53 x 76 centimeters|Scale 1:200,000|General Map Collection
